query:
SELECT 
  u.id as user_id, 
  u.name as user_name, 
  u.email, 
  u.role,
  u.accountStatus,
  m.id as member_id, 
  m.membershipTier,
  m.userId as member_userId
FROM users u 
LEFT JOIN members m ON u.id = m.userId 
WHERE u.name = 'doublecranch2015' OR u.email LIKE '%doublecranch2015%';
